        <cdata>
          <text>&lt;p class="MsoNormal"&gt;&lt;b&gt;Hostage and Wrongful Detainee Day Act of 2023&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p class="MsoNormal"&gt;This bill requests the President to issue an annual proclamation designating Hostage and Wrongful Detainee Day. The bill also designates the Hostage and Wrongful Detainee Flag as a symbol of the commitment of the United States to recognizing citizens held as hostages or wrongfully detained abroad.&lt;/p&gt;</text>
        </cdata>
      </summary>
